{"tid":1379792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[催淚] 728上環義士：「真子彈我哋都唔會怕，請回應我哋嘅訴求！」","createTime":"2019-07-29T00:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:47:55.000Z","uid":36592,"like":178,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"afbf0c50dcde6c4732bb81b6528267186f615239","tid":1379792,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/leg-09_fKNND_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fleg-09_fKNND_1200x0.png&h=a53f5006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不滿政府的示威者今天在西環至上環一帶與警察的衝突，持續至晚上十時後仍未停止，廿多歲的「大師」雙眼通紅地對《立場新聞》記者說，示威者防線晚上退到林士街停車場附近時，警方除了放催淚彈，還發射橡膠子彈，他旁邊的人手上的木盾「啪」的一聲被打爛，於是他們開始向後跑，他前方一名蒙面示威者倒下，被多人抬到一旁想加以救護，但因只是在停車場對面，防暴警又不斷施放催淚彈，於是他們再把他抬走，當時他應該是清醒的。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「我想同香港政府說：我哋係唔怕你嫁，你出催淚彈、橡膠彈、海棉彈還是真子彈，我哋都唔會怕，請回應我哋嘅訴求，唔好再逃避啦！」他說。「守護香港人的，從來不是政府或警察，從來都只是我哋香港人。只有香港人的地方，才能守護香港人。上街吧！香港人不要再對政府再抱任何幻想。我要講嘅係咁多！」</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: 立場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/728-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E6%A9%A1%E8%86%A0%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E6%AF%81%E6%9C%A8%E7%9B%BE-%E7%9C%9F%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E6%80%95-%E8%AB%8B%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E5%98%85%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F728-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25A9%25A1%25E8%2586%25A0%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%25AF%2581%25E6%259C%25A8%25E7%259B%25BE-%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2580%2595-%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%25E5%2598%2585%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=584da3d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F728-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25A9%25A1%25E8%2586%25A0%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%25AF%2581%25E6%259C%25A8%25E7%259B%25BE-%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2580%2595-%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%25E5%2598%2585%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%2F&h=34c19586\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/728-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E6%A9%A1%E8%86%A0%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E6%AF%81%E6%9C%A8%E7%9B%BE-%E7%9C%9F%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E6%80%95-%E8%AB%8B%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E5%98%85%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82/</a>"},{"pid":"1ad0618a3edf94bc25cfd141d7066fc601ed25bb","tid":1379792,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:35:44.000Z","msg":"真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0e6cb5096a32b4597b87eba16d07fc8801357b","tid":1379792,"uid":275607,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:38:01.000Z","msg":"真係催淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d921443a7d036e38b16a25f93a6b0ccddedaaa","tid":1379792,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:38:11.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96f167fb9e791c101172a6f75dd606c7b26fa3b","tid":1379792,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"