"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:44:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d2bd71e3ff3e408060256d1c50ec9498e3198c0","tid":1379792,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:45:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9adf41d2f0024f8e6d3107ca9139217e6bec915f","tid":1379792,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:45:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e6520b9210029fb320cf350645c0c44dd10a7d70","tid":1379792,"uid":6528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:45:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"3aa0d70a03d9ca56d05961d894d2be65dfe5cd01","tid":1379792,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:49:49.000Z","msg":"守護香港人的，從來不是政府或警察，從來都只是我哋香港人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b06e304a760e04ad0cc69dc107077d03febca51","tid":1379792,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:52:21.000Z","msg":"有交稅既先係老闆，<br />\n<br />\n你會唔會向幫你打工既提出訴求？<br />\n<br />\n下次可以講&quot;要求&quot;，<br />\n<br />\n記住市民先係老闆，<br />\n<br />\n講完。"},{"pid":"54aa0b722192afd3ea0cbd4f61462f5083312d35","tid":1379792,"uid":38237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:52:42.000Z","msg":"--------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打爆啲交通燈會唔會易過全民死火燈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------"},{"pid":"04c2a022e13e38f4b70eb17dd3151d32acf95899","tid":1379792,"uid":89834,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:53:56.000Z","msg":"型到<br />\n不過一開實彈咪又係人踩人"},{"pid":"b205a47bf716ca2e47ca36d77937cc5a74816822","tid":1379792,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"Tvb呢？去撚左邊"},{"pid":"52323ade8345faf8a6af8bf63afa51a8bfdd882b","tid":1379792,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f63f62a4d80454483235bccc85d762854cc313","tid":1379792,"uid":231594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset